</g>
</svg>
</span><p>You can design your own digital signage with free digital signage software.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-barbershop-section8-step5" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>8.5&nbsp;</span><h4 id=use-search-engine-marketing>Use search engine marketing (SEM).</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-use-search-engine-marketing-288x288-20200817_2020-08-17-092903.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Use search engine marketing (SEM)."></div></div><p>These days, people most often find businesses by asking their phone about it. If you want to appear when someone asks "Where is the nearest barbershop?" be sure to register for Google My Business. Also, consider setting up a Yelp! page and asking happy customers to rate your business there.</p><div
class="step-tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
d="M256,0C114.844,0,0,114.844,0,256s114.844,256,256,256s256-114.844,256-256S397.156,0,256,0z M298.667,416    c0,5.896-4.771,10.667-10.667,10.667h-64c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667V256h-10.667c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667    v-42.667c0-5.896,4.771-10.667,10.667-10.667H288c5.896,0,10.667,4.771,10.667,10.667V416z M256,170.667    c-23.531,0-42.667-19.135-42.667-42.667S232.469,85.333,256,85.333s42.667,19.135,42.667,42.667S279.531,170.667,256,170.667z" data-original="#000000" class="active-path" data-old_color="#000000" fill="#4949E7"/>
</g>
</svg>
</span><p>Pay-per-click advertising and optimizing your website for search can also have huge payoffs, but you'll either need to research these topics or hire a local agency to help you.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-barbershop-section8-step6" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>8.6&nbsp;</span><h4 id=host-a-grand-opening>Host a grand opening.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-have-a-grand-opening-288x288-20200817.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Host a grand opening."></div></div><p>A grand opening is a good opportunity to introduce your shop to the community and to attract attention. Be sure to advertise your grand opening in the local paper and on social media. You could also start handing out flyers a week or so in advance. You want as many people there as possible.</p><div
class="step-tip">
<span
class="icon">
