817.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2","height":"288","width":"288"}},{"@type":"HowToStep","position":"3","name":"<p>Describe your launch.<\/p>\n","text":"<p>State when you would like to launch, if you will be hosting a launch party, and if you are offering opening specials.<\/p>\n","url":"https://www.zarla.com/guides/how-to-start-a-barbershop#how-to-start-a-barbershop-section2-step3","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-describe-your-launch-288x288-20200817.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2","height":"288","width":"288"}},{"@type":"HowToStep","position":"4","name":"<p>List your sources of revenue.<\/p>\n","text":"<p>Let investors know how you will be earning money. Your main form of income will be from grooming services, but you could also sell hair and beard products.<\/p>\n","url":"https://www.zarla.com/guides/how-to-start-a-barbershop#how-to-start-a-barbershop-section2-step4","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-explain-your-source-of-revenue-288x288-20200812.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2","height":"288","width":"288"}},{"@type":"HowToStep","position":"5","name":"<p>List your essential staff.<\/p>\n","text":"<p>List the job titles of roles you will need to be filled when you launch the business.<\/p>\n<p>Staff members you may need include:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Barbers.<\/li>\n<li>A receptionist.<\/li>\n<li>Cleaning staff.<\/li>\n<li>A barista (if you offer coffee).<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n","url":"https://www.zarla.com/guides/how-to-start-a-barbershop#how-to-start-a-barbershop-section2-step5","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-list-your-essential-staff-288x288-20200817.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2","height":"288","width":"288"}},{"@type":"HowToStep","position":"6","name":"<p>Describe your marketing strategy.<\/p>\n","text":"<p>Explain how you will market your business using social media, flyers, or paid advertisements on Google.<\/p>\n<p>This section 